            <m>\limit{x}{1}{\frac{x^a-1}{x-1}}</m> (Assume <m>a</m> is a
            positive integer.)
          </p>
        </statement>
        <answer>
          <p>
            <m>\limit{x}{1}{\frac{x^a-1}{x-1}}=a </m>
          </p>
        </answer>
      </exercise>
      <exercise>
